you to our Books

00:00:28.330 --> 00:00:29.930
and Beyond Series
this afternoon.

00:00:29.930 --> 00:00:34.370
It is our final one of this
season, so we're thrilled,

00:00:34.370 --> 00:00:36.550
very thrilled with the
special conversation we have

00:00:36.550 --> 00:00:39.250
for you today to
complete our season

00:00:39.250 --> 00:00:42.750
